<example xml:id="ex-add">
<statement>
<p>Let <m>\vect{a} = [5, 1]</m> and <m>\vect{b} = [-2, 3]</m>. Algebraically, 
	<m>\vect{a} + \vect{b} = [5 + (-2), 1 + 3] = [3, 4]</m>. 
We can also calculate this geometrically, which is done in <xref ref="fig-vadd"/>, giving the 
same answer that <m>\vect{a} + \vect{b} = [3, 4]</m>.
</p>

